{
  "texts": [
    "Edge AI, or the execution of machine learning models locally on edge devices, is reshaping intrusion detection by allowing for the detection of threats in real time without the need for centralized servers.",
    "Edge AI is crucial for securing the network at the device level in the age of IoT (Internet of Things) and edge computing, when billions of devices are interconnected.",
    "Deployed intrusion detection models on edge devices may rapidly assess network traffic and device behavior, enabling swift action against security threats 51.",
    "When low-latency intrusion detection is crucial and centralized systems are at risk of being attacked, this method becomes indispensable.",
    "Homomorphic encryption is a game-changer for intrusion detection since it allows for secure data analysis without the risk of sensitive information disclosure."
  ]
}